Biography

Pete Wentz is an American musician who is the bassist and lyricist for the rock band Fall Out Boy.[1]

Peter Lewis Kingston Wentz III was born on 05 Jun 1979 in Wilmette, Cook County, Illinois, USA and is the son of Roy Wentz and Dale Lewis.

Peter "Pete" Lewis Kingston Wentz, III married Ashley "Ashlee" Nicole Simpson on 17 May 2008 in Encino, California, USA at the home of the bride's parents with her father officiating the ceremony. They divorced in 2011.
